---
// /pages/about-platform.astro
import LayoutSidebar from '../../app/LayoutSidebar.astro';
import GelymarLogo from '../../assets/gelymar.svg';
---

<LayoutSidebar>
  <section class="relative w-full px-6 py-16 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200  dark:bg-gray-900 font-sans animate-fade-in-up">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-12">
        <GelymarLogo class="h-20 w-auto mb-4" />
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#002E50] dark:text-white text-center">
          About the Gelymar Platform
        </h1>
        <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-[#F6B234] mt-4 rounded"></div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg text-center leading-relaxed mb-10">
        The Gelymar Web Platform is a comprehensive document and logistics management system that supports export operations based on Chilean seaweed derivatives. It ensures regulatory compliance, operational efficiency, and strengthened communication with clients.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#00538C] mb-3">Core Modules</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong>User Access Management</strong>: Login for administrators and clients with permission levels.</li>
            <li><strong>Client Management</strong>: Maintain clients, consignees, contact emails, and destinations.</li>
            <li><strong>Operations & Documents</strong>: View and upload documents by order, customer, or date.</li>
            <li><strong>Internal Document Generation</strong>: Packing Lists and Customs Mandates as fillable PDFs.</li>
            <li><strong>Document Repository</strong>: Auto-created folders per client with historical views.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#00538C] mb-3">Smart Automation</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Automated Notifications</strong> for order receipt, shipping, and arrival updates.</li>
            <li><strong>PDF Generation</strong> from SAP data and templates with email-ready formats.</li>
            <li><strong>Partial Shipments</strong>: Track partial deliveries with segmented labels (A, B, C...).</li>
            <li><strong>KPI Dashboard</strong> with graphical indicators and customs agency reports.</li>
            <li><strong>Client Communication</strong> through messaging and notification system (chat, optional bot).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#00538C] mb-3">Platform Standards</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Security</strong>: Role-based access, secure email handling, and data validation.</li>
          <li><strong>Compatibility</strong>: Integrated with SAP and works on major browsers.</li>
          <li><strong>Performance</strong>: Automated processes by date, type and destination.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    @keyframes fade-in-up {
      0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .animate-fade-in-up {
      animation: fade-in-up 0.8s ease-out both;
    }
  </style>
</LayoutSidebar>